metadata.name: The Illusion of Love
metadata.description:
What are real feelings for us? 

It can't be put into words, it can't be shown.

Valeria's soul is tired after love where we are hurt. 
We get pain with every thrown word and close ourselves to true love, we begin to build illusions and with this photo, we show that our illusions do not allow us to open up and understand what true love is because it is so deep and complex that not everyone can touch them. 

Therefore, we touch an artificial illusion than something real.
